data.description: Welcome home! If you have been waiting for something move-in ready AND affordable, look no further. This updated rambler is ready for its new owner! Featuring almost 1100 sqft and offering 2 beds, 2baths, with a 2 car garage, you will absolutely fall in love with this layout. A commuters dream, minutes from multiple highways, downtown Seattle, and the Seatac airport! New flooring, paint, updated kitchen, bathrooms, this super cute opportunity will be sure to impress even the pickiest buyers! A fully fenced and cozy private yard allows you space to enjoy the sun but not be burdened with hours of yardwork. This is truly a must-see home that will not last long! Hurry and make your appointment to view!
